nodes.text: Dynym Quid was an alien that spent time in the Canto Casino in the city of Canto Bight on the planet Cantonica in 34 ABY. While the Resistance agents Finn and Rose Tico searched the casino for the Master Codebreaker, Quid stood at one of the establishment's bars with a human woman and caressed her hand. The building then briefly shook around them as several fathiers raced past on the nearby Canto Bight racetrack.
Quid had gray skin and two blue eyes, with a series of brown-tipped chin tentacles, and two arms ending in five-fingered hands. The alien wore a black robe at the casino.
Dynym Quid first appeared in the 2017 sequel trilogy film, Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, and was first identified in the 2018 magazine Star Wars: The Last Jedi The Official Movie Companion.
